==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Yezdegerdian
<hw>Yez`de*ger"di*an</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to <ets>Yezdegerd</ets>, the last Sassanian monarch of
Persia, who was overthrown by the Muslims; <as>as, the
<ex>Yezdegerdian</ex> era, which began on the 16th of June, <sc>a.
d.</sc> 632. The era is still used by the Parsees</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yezdi</ent>⟦br⟧
